Availability
Energy International Power Marketing Corp. (EIP) makes electric energy and capacity available under this Rate Schedule to any purchaser for resale.
Applicability
This Rate Schedule is applicable to all sales of energy or capacity by EIP not otherwise subject to a particular rate schedule of EIP.
Rates
All sales shall be made at rates established by agreement between the purchaser and EIP.
Other Terms and Conditions
All other terms and conditions shall be established by agreement between the purchaser and EIP.
Affiliate Sales Prohibited
No sale may be made pursuant to this Rate Schedule to any public utility with a franchised electric service territory that is controlled by or under common control with or controlling EIP.
Effective Date
This Rate Schedule is effective on the date specified by the commission.
